<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/anneliese-dodds> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Anneliese Dodds was Minister for Development at the Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office and Minister for Women and Equalities at the Department for Education from 8 July 2024 until 28 February 2025. She was elected as the MP for Oxford East in June 2017. Follow Anneliese on X/Twitter: @AnnelieseDodds"@en .
